  <!-- Tutorial -->
  <RimRim_Tutorial_Title>Quick Start</RimRim_Tutorial_Title>
  <RimRim_Tutorial_Body>1. Select a ThingDef from the left panel.\n2. Drag-and-drop PNG files onto layers to assign textures.\n3. Use the Inspector to tweak position, scale, rotation and color.\n4. Press F5 to hot-reload changes into the live game.\n5. Use File → Save Preset to store your work.\n6. Use File → Export XML to write patched Defs to disk.</RimRim_Tutorial_Body>
